  <brief_title>The Efficacy and Safety of the Combination of Tamsulosin and Tadalafil in Men With Lower Urinary Tract Symptoms Due to Benign Prostatic Hyperplasia and Erectile Dysfunction</brief_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
