  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The efficacy and safety of the combination of tamsulosin and tadalafil in men with lower
      urinary tract symptoms due to benign prostatic hyperplasia and Erectile Dysfunction: a
      randomized, double blinded, parallel design, active controlled, multi-center, phase 3
      clinical trial
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
